{
  "title": "Savory Kenyan Lamb Stew",
  "description": "A tangy and springy Kenyan dish featuring makrut lime leaves and long-fermentation-dough, perfect for meal prep. This dash-friendly recipe is cooked in a wok.",
  "cuisine": "Kenyan",
